        <div class="mhero">
          <div class="micon"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M22 11.08V12a10 10 0 11-5.93-9.14"/><polyline points="22 4 12 14.01 9 11.01"/></svg></div>
          <div class="mh">Sarah, welcome to Communities! 🎉</div>
          <div class="msub">Your courses, community, and students — all in one place. Your content has been migrated and is ready to go. Let's take a quick tour.</div>
        </div>
        <div class="mstats">
          <div class="mstat"><div class="mstat-emoji">🎓</div><div class="mstat-n">4</div><div class="mstat-l">Courses migrated</div></div>
          <div class="mstat"><div class="mstat-emoji">✅</div><div class="mstat-n">100%</div><div class="mstat-l">Content intact</div></div>
          <div class="mstat"><div class="mstat-emoji">🔒</div><div class="mstat-n">Creator</div><div class="mstat-l">Access only</div></div>
        </div>
        <div class="mfooter">
          <button class="mbtn-skip" onclick="closeModal()">Skip for now</button>
          <button class="mbtn-go" onclick="goStep(2)">Show me around →</button>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="modal-step" id="ms2">
