          <div class="mh">Here's what's waiting for you</div>
          <div class="msub">Your migrated content lives across these key areas. We're in creator-only testing right now — student migration is coming very soon.</div>
        </div>
        <div class="mtile-grid">
          <div class="mtile" onclick="showToast('Head to Courses in the left nav!')">
            <div class="mtile-emoji">🎓</div>
            <div class="mtile-t">Courses</div>
            <div class="mtile-s">All 4 migrated courses, modules and drip schedules</div>
            <div class="mtile-arr">›</div>
          </div>
          <div class="mtile mtile-locked">
            <div class="mtile-emoji">👥</div>
