            <div class="mtile-s">Migrate your students once creator testing is complete</div>
            <div class="locked-fog"><div class="locked-pill">🔒 Coming soon</div></div>
          </div>
          <div class="mtile" onclick="showToast('Head to Communities in the left nav!')">
            <div class="mtile-emoji">💬</div>
            <div class="mtile-t">Community Feed</div>
            <div class="mtile-s">Post updates and get ready to welcome your students</div>
            <div class="mtile-arr">›</div>
          </div>
          <div class="mtile" onclick="showToast('Set up gamification in your community settings!')">
